name: TELEPORT64
description:
First Person Shooter where each time you hit an enemy you teleport to i

Features:

  • Fast-paced FPS controls
  • AutoTeleport1000 to automatically teleport you to an enemy you hit
  • Awful "programmer" art (made a little better because of nice free arts I found)
  • And that's all, folks!

Controls [Keyboard & Mouse / Gamepad]

  • Movement: WASD / Left Stick
  • Jump: Space bar / South Button
  • Shoot: Left Mouse Button / Right Shoulder Button
  • Reload: ESC / Select

Made in more or less 2 weeks for LOWREZJAM 2021 by dino460.
